Ing '''Xiamen''' ({{IPA-cmn|ɕjâmə̌n}}), a mayayaus muring '''Amoy''' {{IPAc-en|ə|ˈ|m|ɔɪ}},<ref>{{OED|Amoy}}</ref> metung yang manimunang lakanbalen king [[mauli]] [[aslagan]] a bebe dayatmalat king [[Taiwan Strait]] ning [[Maldang Republika ning Tsina]]. Panibalan de antimong [[sub-provincial city]] ning lalawigan ning [[Fujian]] a maki lapad a {{convert|1699.39|km2}} ampong populasyun a 3.67 milyun. Maki leparan yang urbanisadung ngeni mas maragul kesa ketang urban a isla at sasakup kareng anggang anam a distritu ning ([[Huli District|Huli]], [[Siming]], [[Jimei]], [[Tong'an]], [[Haicang District|Haicang]] at bayu-bayu pamu, ing [[Xiang'an]]). Kalele ne ing [[Quanzhou]] king [[pangulu]] ampo ing [[Zhangzhou]], at uli na niti bibilug yang leparan a urbanisadung maki maygit limang milyung katau. Ala la mang {{convert|10|km}} karayu deng islang [[Jinmen]] (Kinmen) a panibalan ning [[Taiwan|Republika ning Tsina (Taiwan)]].   

